---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
	<section class="px-4 pb-20 pt-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
			<p class="mb-5 font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-400">Current architecture</p>
			<h1 class="max-w-5xl text-5xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
				ResonantOS is becoming a community-owned system governed by ResonantDAO.
			</h1>
			<p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-8 text-zinc-300">
				The new foundation is not a liquid token or a transferable badge. It is an official, non-transferable membership credential that proves a wallet belongs to the DAO and can access DAO smart contracts.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
				<a href="/membership" class="rounded-md bg-emerald-600 px-6 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-emerald-500">Explore Membership</a>
				<a href="/dao" class="rounded-md border border-white/15 px-6 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-zinc-100 transition-colors hover:border-emerald-400/70">Read DAO Model</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="credentials" class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">The Credential Stack</h2>
			<p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-zinc-400">
				These NFTs are official DAO-issued credentials. Each one is locked to the wallet that receives it and cannot be sold, transferred, or used by another account.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-10 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
				<a href="/manifesto" class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6 transition-colors hover:border-emerald-400/50">
					<p class="font-mono text-sm text-emerald-400">01</p>
					<h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold">Augmentatism Manifesto NFT</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">Proof that the wallet signed and agreed to the canonical Augmentatism Manifesto.</p>
				</a>
				<a href="/membership" class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6 transition-colors hover:border-emerald-400/50">
					<p class="font-mono text-sm text-emerald-400">02</p>
					<h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold">Community Member NFT</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">The DAO access credential. One active Community NFT per wallet, verified through the official MemberRecord.</p>
				</a>
				<a href="/symbiotic-license" class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6 transition-colors hover:border-emerald-400/50">
					<p class="font-mono text-sm text-emerald-400">03</p>
					<h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold">Symbiotic Licence NFT</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">A non-transferable licence and co-ownership credential for eligible Community Members.</p>
				</a>
				<a href="/pioneer" class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6 transition-colors hover:border-emerald-400/50">
					<p class="font-mono text-sm text-emerald-400">04</p>
					<h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold">Resonant Pioneer NFT</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">A capped early-adopter credential for the first 1000 eligible Community Members.</p>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="originals" class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.85fr_1.15fr] lg:items-start">
			<div>
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Originals Are Verified On-Chain</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-zinc-400">
					A fake NFT can copy a name, image, or metadata URI. It cannot create a valid membership record under the official ResonantDAO Membership Program.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-emerald-400/20 bg-emerald-400/[0.06] p-6">
				<pre class="overflow-x-auto text-sm leading-7 text-emerald-100"><code>member_record = PDA("member", wallet)

DAO contracts verify:
- signer matches the wallet
- member status is active
- Community NFT mint is recorded
- record belongs to the official program</code></pre>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="roadmap" class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">What Changed</h2>
			<div class="mt-8 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
				<div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">DAO-first</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">The public website now centers the membership and governance layer instead of the older OpenClaw extension pitch.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">No Symbiotic Wallet Yet</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">Human wallet membership comes first. AI wallets, AI Community Members, and Symbiotic Pair Records are later phases.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Contribution Over Capital</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">Governance is designed around verified membership, contribution, reputation, and community trust.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="faq" class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">FAQ</h2>
			<div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
				<details class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
					<summary class="cursor-pointer text-xl font-semibold">Can I transfer my DAO NFTs?</summary>
					<p class="mt-4 text-zinc-400">No. The membership credentials are designed as soulbound Token-2022 credentials. Wallet migration must be a DAO-controlled process, not a normal transfer.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
					<summary class="cursor-pointer text-xl font-semibold">Why does the Community NFT matter?</summary>
					<p class="mt-4 text-zinc-400">It is the access credential other DAO contracts can verify. The contract gate checks the official MemberRecord, not the public metadata.</p>
				</details>
				<details class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
					<summary class="cursor-pointer text-xl font-semibold">Is the built-in AI wallet live?</summary>
					<p class="mt-4 text-zinc-400">No. The Symbiotic Wallet is deferred. The first stage issues membership directly to the user's wallet.</p>
				</details>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
